#Negation lan perfective verb
Source: b:13
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena: {negation}
alwaladu		la 		    yakula			altuffahata
al-walad-u		la 		    yakul-a			al-tuffahat-a
DEF-boy-NOM		not		    eat-PERF	DEF-apple-ACC
‘The boy will not eat the apple.’


